lead_paragraph: Nirra Fields scored 17 of her 24 points in the fourth quarter to rally No. 15 UCLA to a 69-63 win over Utah on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Fields Sparks No. 15 UCLA Women Past Utah 69-63
